Mercari Japan’s biggest community-powered e-commerce application that allows individuals
to easily buy and sell goods.
• Need - High prized items are not sold easily, in low prized items seller lose money.
• Possible solution - Users can do market research, however it takes lot of effort and this idea
may not occur to new Mercari users.
• ML Solution created using EDA, Data tranformation, TfIdf vectorizer,One hot encoding, stopwords
removal, Models like Ridge and Lasso regression, XgBoost, SVR, stacking, Grid search for
hyper parameter tuning, Model combinations etc.
• Obtained RMSLE accuracy of 0.42778.
